<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/messaging.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="loginhome">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
<!--         <p>You have succesfully joined a chat with <%= user.firstname %>!</p> -->

    </div>
        <table style="width:100%">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <div class="chatsection">
                        <h3 id="timer">Chat expires in <span id="timeLeft"></span></h3>
                        <div class="chat">
                            <ul class="messages" id='messages'>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="typing">Other user is typing. . .</div>
                            <div id="entermessage">
                                <form action="">
                                    <input id="m" placeholder="Enter Message" autocomplete="off" /><button id="send">Send</button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td class="infocol">
                    <h3><strong>Information:</strong></h3>
                    <div class='infosection'>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Bridges 2 and Helipad in Mountain Island have been broken (indicated by the warning signs).</li>
                            <li>The travel times for the helicopter are as follows:
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Mainland <-> Village Island 5 min (each way)</li>
                                    <li>Mainland <-> Mountain Island 5 min (each way)</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>Repairs times for road crew takes 5 minutes.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <img src="images/map.jpg">
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="messageBottom" id="closeChatSection">
            <button id="opencloseChat">CloseChat</button>
            <p>Please only close the chat if you are completely finished. Both users must close the chat to have it finish prematurely.</p>
        </div>

    <div class="messageBottom" id="beginSurvey">
        <p>Please fill out the survery below and email in your consent form to <strong>mattwoicik@gmail.com</strong> to recieve compensation if you have not done so already. Thank you for participating!</p>
        <a href="https://goo.gl/forms/UMMX8mKzoNw3wtBc2" target="_blank"><button id="returnHome">Fill out Survery</button></a>
    </div>

    <div class="useractionpopup" id="timewarning">
      <div>
        <span class="closebox">&times;</span>
        <h1>5 Minute Warning</h1>
        <p class="levelinfo">Warning, you have 5 minutes or less remaining for this conversation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="useractionpopup" id="closechatpop">
      <div>
        <span class="closebox">&times;</span>
        <h1>Warning</h1>
        <p class="levelinfo">Warning, are you sure you want to close the chat? Make sure you have concluded the task at hand.</p>
        <button id="closeChat">Close Chat</button>
        <button class="closebox">Cancel</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>











